                    <p class="card-text">Assign admin roles to your support team and assign the complete experience of ticket cloud.</p>
                  </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-deck justify-content-center text-center">
                <div class="card smart-card diffuse-shadow box-hover">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <img src="/images/message.svg" alt="email notification icon" class="about-icons">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Email Notifications</h5>
                      <p class="card-text">Get notified everytime a new ticket is raised. Our Notification System also notifies users about the current status of tickets and enables support team to send emails on-demand!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card smart-card diffuse-shadow box-hover">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <img src="/images/planner.svg" alt="time report icon" class="about-icons">
                      <h5 class="card-title">Response Time Reports</h5>
                      <p class="card-text">Generate immediate reports for response and resolve times of user tickets. Get complete report of resolve time once the ticket is resolved.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
